Q17_4|Read each of the following statements and decide how much you agree with each according to your beliefs and experiences. - I dislike questions which could be answered in many different ways.|閱讀以下每個陳述，並根據你的信念和經驗決定你對每個陳述的同意程度。 我討厭可以用多種不同方式回答的問題。。
